We are seeking a Business Development Manager to be located in our Singapore office. This position requires an ambitious individual to focus on four key areas: (1) developing new client relationships for the firm in the Asia region, both emerging companies and more mature growth oriented companies; (2) retaining existing clients; (3) cross selling existing clients; and (4) raising our Firm's profile in the Asian market among key influencers.
Candidates must have a bachelor's degree and 5+ years of sales and/or business development experience, preferably in a professional services organization, with proven ability to generate and convert sales leads. Preferred candidates will have a depth of understanding of the individual office’s region and experience with sales contact database programs. We offer a competitive compensation and excellent benefits package. EOE.